    <p dir="ltr">Hi there,</p>
    Thank you for signing up and creating your profile. We realize that your time is valuable. Let&#39;s right away get to the meat of it.
    <p dir="ltr">What can you do with your profile account:</p>
    <ol>
      <li aria-level="1" dir="ltr">
        <p dir="ltr" role="presentation">You can leave a review to your doctors, appreciate constructive criticism if needed.&nbsp;</p>
      </li>
      <li aria-level="1" dir="ltr">
        <p dir="ltr" role="presentation">You can shortlist your favourite group of doctors and save this list in your account. This helps when you are shopping to find a doctor that meets your criteria.&nbsp;</p>
      </li>
      <li aria-level="1" dir="ltr">
        <p dir="ltr" role="presentation">You will be eligible to receive any member discounts that FindMyDirectDoctor plans to implement in the future.<br />
          &nbsp;</p>
